<p>In today&rsquo;s Mac Geek Gab episode, John and Dave talk through all the places to check when repurposing a Mac for another person. Then it&rsquo;s off to manage the iOS Notification center, and finally your favorite geeks go through a group of questions and comments about their recent <a href="http://www.macobserver.com/tmo/podcast/mgg_388_backup_strategies_cool_stuff_found/" data-wpel-link="internal">backup episode</a>. All this and more in today&rsquo;s podcast.</p>
